# Project Structure

This is a Next.js 15 web application with Tailwind CSS for styling and PayloadCMS for content management.

## Main Directories

- [src/app/(frontend)](mdc:src/app/(frontend)) - Contains frontend components, pages, styles, and utilities
- [src/app/(payload)](mdc:src/app/(payload)) - Contains PayloadCMS admin panel and API routes
- [src/collections](mdc:src/collections) - PayloadCMS collections (data models)
- [public](mdc:public) - Static assets

## Key Configuration Files

- [next.config.mjs](mdc:next.config.mjs) - Next.js configuration
- [postcss.config.ts](mdc:postcss.config.ts) - PostCSS configuration for Tailwind
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Project dependencies
- [payload.config.ts](mdc:src/payload.config.ts) - PayloadCMS configuration
